*[[毛帶蟹屬|毛帶蟹屬]] ''Dotilla'' <small>Stimpson, 1858</small>
*''[[Dotilloplax|Dotilloplax]]'' <small>Tweedie, 1950</small>
*''[[Dotillopsis|Dotillopsis]]'' <small>Kemp, 1919</small>
*[[泥蟹属|泥蟹属]] ''Ilyoplax'' <small>Stimpson, 1858</small> 
*''[[Potamocypoda|Potamocypoda]]'' <small>Tweedie, 1938</small>
*''[[Pseudogelasimus|Pseudogelasimus]]'' <small>Tweedie, 1937</small>
*[[股窗蟹屬|股窗蟹屬]] ''Scopimera'' <small>De Haan, 1835</small><ref>{{cite journal |url=http://ntur.lib.ntu.edu.tw/handle/246246/247900 |title=東亞地區股窗蟹(甲殼類：十足目：毛帶蟹科)之 多樣性，系統分類及親緣關係研究 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2013-04-27 |authorlink1=王展豪 |first1=Kingsley J.H. |last1=Wong |authorlink2=陳國勤 |first2=Benny K.K. |last2=Chan }}</ref>
*''[[Shenius|Shenius]]'' <small>Serène, 1971</small>
*[[切腹蟹屬|切腹蟹屬]] ''Tmethypocoelis'' <small>Koelbel, 1897</small>

